  "id": "RAW_a234d506",
  "title": "有意思小周刊 No.163（2026.01.26）：AI_Coding 长文分享：如何真正把工具用起来，从原理到实践",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxODA0Mzg0Mg==&mid=2649452154&idx=1&sn=a27f6bb82d03610bd7d108b089aed710",
  "date": "2026-01-26 00:30:00",
